{"tid":1548260,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【黃雀行動】勇武是蟬、黑警是螂、和理是雀！停止散播死人恐慌！","createTime":"2019-09-07T03:23:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T07:03:43.000Z","uid":167548,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"13889faad21638664f65720224db868200ea06f2","tid":1548260,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:23:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">螳螂捕蟬、黃雀在後。</span></strong></span><br />\n勇武喻為<span style=\"color: orange;\">蟬</span>。<br />\n黑警喻為<span style=\"color: blue;\">螂</span>。<br />\n和理喻為<span style=\"color: orange;\">雀</span>。<br />\n從今往後，每一名「勇武」/「活躍和理非」都一定要有一位<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>在明</strong></span>「聯絡員」，再加一位<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>在暗</strong></span>「黃雀」。請每一次行動前聯絡<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>兩</strong></span>位固定 至友 但必定 非至親。以Telegram作聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n每一次聯絡前必須交代自身暗號，再作交流同埋報平安。<br />\n<br />\n倘若行動之後失去聯絡（早起的黃雀有蟲吃 = 事態平靜後翌日早上6時/心急盡早搵律師）, 請唔好慌張。「聯絡員」搵左律師先。<br />\n<br />\n假如背後真正「黃雀」一直收唔到「聯絡員」報平安搵到勇武，請立刻沉著應爆，時機成熟<span style=\"color: red;\">（至少72小時）</span>就爆料比蘋果，立法會議員。<br />\n<br />\n「勇武」搵「黃雀」同埋「聯絡員」番嚟。但是「黃雀」單方面認識「聯絡員」, 反之不認識。<br />\n「黃雀」透過「勇武」得到「勇武」同埋「聯絡員」資料。"},{"pid":"52f29a8bd41b979fcb492769834080545f4d9d9b","tid":1548260,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:23:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d00ff17a910e23731fcc4224b5d4bb90c3a39e0c","tid":1548260,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T03:24:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">麻煩出去幫手推哂908 既post上黎，我P牌推唔到</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">九月八日 星期日<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">1:30pm遮打 ----&gt;  2pm美國領事館</span> </span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span s